  "industry_note": "UNS R30075 (cast F75) / R31537 (wrought F1537) / ISO 5832-12 — biomedical Co-28Cr-6Mo alloy. Wrought Hot-rolled bar: σy 590 / UTS 1100 / El 20%. Cold-worked (wire): σy 825 / UTS 1240 / El 15%. Tmax 600°C continuous. 가장 흔한 의료 임플란트 (artificial hip head / knee femoral component / dental crown), AM LPBF (EOS Cobalt-Chrome SP2 = ASTM F75). 매우 wear-resistant + 부식 저항.",
